<section class="page-content reveal">
  <div class="container narrow reveal">
    <p>
      This website is provided by ImperialPaws Pekingese to share puppy
      availability, explain the adoption process, receive applications, provide
      status tracking, and prepare clear invoices for approved buyers.
    </p>

    <h2>Puppy Availability</h2>
    <p>
      Puppy availability, photos, descriptions, prices, and status labels may
      change as applications are reviewed and placement decisions are made.
      Submitting an application does not reserve a puppy or guarantee approval.
    </p>

    <h2>Applications</h2>
    <p>
      Applications are reviewed individually. The website prevents the same buyer
      from submitting repeated applications for the same puppy when the same email
      address or phone number is used.
    </p>

    <h2>Invoices and Payments</h2>
    <p>
      Invoices are created only after an application is approved. A public puppy
      page or application form should not be treated as a payment request.
      Approved buyers should review invoice details carefully before taking next
      steps.
    </p>

    <h2>Responsible Placement</h2>
    <p>
      ImperialPaws Pekingese may decline, pause, or continue reviewing an
      application when doing so supports the welfare of the puppy and the
      suitability of the placement.
    </p>

    <h2>Website Use</h2>
    <p>
      Visitors should use the website truthfully and respectfully. Automated
      abuse, false applications, unauthorized admin access attempts, or misuse of
      invoice links is not permitted.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>
